{"id":"jashub","term":"Jashub","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Returner. (1.) The third of Issachar’s four sons (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 7:1\">1 Chr. 7:1</a>); called also Job (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 46:13\">Gen. 46:13</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 10:29\">Ezra 10:29</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 7:1","Genesis 46:13","Ezra 10:29"]}